sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeGW as KServe Ingress<br/>Gateway API / HTTPRoute
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HTTP as vllm-spyre (HTTP)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant gRPC as vllm-spyre (gRPC)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>PVC / S3 (443/TCP)
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (optional)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-Compatible API)
    Client->>KServeGW: POST /v1/completions<br/>or /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS
    KServeGW->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>Platform-managed routing
    RBAC->>HTTP: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext (localhost)<br/>Auth: proxy-authenticated
    HTTP->>HTTP: vLLM engine processes<br/>on IBM Spyre accelerator
    HTTP-->>RBAC: JSON Response<br/>(completion result)
    RBAC-->>KServeGW: HTTPS Response
    KServeGW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS Protocol)
    Client->>KServeGW: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>TGIS protocol<br/>HTTPS
    KServeGW->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>Platform-managed routing
    RBAC->>gRPC: gRPC request<br/>plaintext (localhost)<br/>Auth: proxy-authenticated
    gRPC->>gRPC: vLLM engine processes<br/>on IBM Spyre accelerator
    gRPC-->>RBAC: gRPC Response<br/>(generated tokens)
    RBAC-->>KServeGW: HTTPS Response
    KServeGW-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over HTTP,HF: Flow 3: Model Loading (startup)
    alt Model from PVC
        HTTP->>Storage: Read model weights<br/>Filesystem mount<br/>No network (volume)
        Storage-->>HTTP: Model artifacts
    else Model from S3
        HTTP->>Storage: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
        Storage-->>HTTP: Model artifacts (TLS 1.2+)
    else Model from Hugging Face
        HTTP->>HF: GET model files<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
        HF-->>HTTP: Model artifacts (TLS 1.2+)
    end
    HTTP->>HTTP: Load model onto<br/>IBM Spyre accelerator

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: Health Check
    Client->>HTTP: GET /health<br/>HTTP/8000
    HTTP-->>Client: 200 OK
